    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section class="section section--soft">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section__head reveal"><h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2></div>
        <div class="faq reveal">
          <div class="faq__item" aria-expanded="false">
            <button class="faq__q">How do you keep our data secure and confidential?<svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg></button>
            <div class="faq__a"><p>We operate under your confidentiality and NDA requirements as standard, signed before any data is shared. Access is limited to your assigned specialist and account manager, and we follow agreed handling, storage, and access controls for every workflow.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq__item" aria-expanded="false">
            <button class="faq__q">Are you GDPR compliant?<svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg></button>
            <div class="faq__a"><p>Yes. We handle personal data strictly as a data processor on your instructions, in line with GDPR principles. We will sign a Data Processing Agreement (DPA) on request and apply the access, retention, and confidentiality controls your business requires.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq__item" aria-expanded="false">
            <button class="faq__q">Which time zones do you cover?<svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg></button>
            <div class="faq__a"><p>We are based in Nairobi (GMT+3) and work comfortably across UK, European, and US business hours. We agree your preferred working window and reporting cadence during onboarding, so there is meaningful daily overlap with your team.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq__item" aria-expanded="false">
            <button class="faq__q">What is the contract length and can we cancel?<svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg></button>
            <div class="faq__a"><p>Engagements run month to month after the one-time setup. There is no long lock-in&mdash;you can scale up, scale down, or give notice in line with the simple terms agreed at onboarding. The 40-hour trial lets you confirm fit before you commit fully.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq__item" aria-expanded="false">
            <button class="faq__q">What happens if we need more capacity?<svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg></button>
            <div class="faq__a"><p>Each pod is one dedicated specialist at 160 hours per month. As your volume grows you can add specialists&mdash;capacity flexes with your needs without new hiring or training cycles on your side.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq__item" aria-expanded="false">
            <button class="faq__q">What tools and systems do you work with?<svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg></button>
            <div class="faq__a"><p>Our specialists work across virtually any format or system&mdash;CRMs, spreadsheets, databases, ticketing and back-office platforms. We onboard to your existing tools during Phase 2 rather than forcing you onto ours.</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

